message.body: Hi John! How are you? I miss you! Jenny said you might e in Philly soon?
Hey Sam! I'm doing good, especially since it's nice and warm today.
I'll be in Philadelphia on the 15th and the 16th! I hope you're free on that Sunday.
I think I should be free that day. Glad you're doing well! Things are okay here. We just had a couple snow days which put me behind on my schedule, yuck. Haha
Yeah, Baltimore got hit with 9 inches or so on Thursday.
Oh gosh, that's awful! We got 7.5 and it's finally melting.
